            <lg xml:id="TK592">
<l>ūkka muṭaimai yuṭaimai poruḷuṭaimai </l>
<l>nillātu nīṅki viṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The possession of (energy of) mind is true property the possession of wealth passes away and abides not.</l>
